    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Upon reaching 11th level, the power of your draconic spirit now radiates from you, warding your allies or inspiring fear in your enemies. As long as you have at least 1 ki point you radiate with draconic power in a 10 feet area around you in one of two ways. You can change which aspect of the aura you radiate when you complete a short or long rest, or when you unleash it (as described below). You can choose to suppress this aura (no action required).</p><p>Furthermore, as a bonus action, you can unleash your draconic power increasing the aura to 30 feet for 1 minute.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.V8y6h9rw0OlDWNIk]{Aspect of the Wyrm: Frightful Presence}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.vydgHUHcHmDAlOzq]{Aspect of the Wyrm: Resistance}</p><p></p>",
